      <p>To import external markdown content just use the <code>md</code> markdown helper with a variable template for the content you want to import, like: <code>\{{{md content}}}</code> (make sure you use the triple staches if you want it escaped).</p>

      <p>Then run <code>grunt assemble</code> to compile it to HTML.</p>

